    autonumber
    actor Buyer as Organization owner/admin
    participant UI as Marketplace UI
    participant API as Marketplace finance API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL + forced RLS
    participant Stripe as Stripe Checkout/Webhook
    actor Creator as Creator owner
    actor Admin as Global admin

    Note over UI,DB: 9.1 Free product
    Buyer->>UI: Approve permissions and install
    UI->>API: Optional free checkout
    API->>DB: Completed zero-value purchase + entitlement + ledger
    API-->>UI: Entitlement active
    UI->>API: Install approved version
    API->>DB: Verify gates and create installation

    Note over UI,Stripe: 9.2 Paid product
    Buyer->>UI: Purchase paid listing/version
    UI->>API: Create checkout
    API->>DB: Pending purchase + receipt + tax metadata
    API->>Stripe: Create one-time Checkout Session
    Stripe-->>UI: Hosted checkout URL
    Stripe->>API: Signed checkout.session.completed
    API->>DB: Verify amount/currency/status and grant entitlement
    UI->>API: Install with purchase_id
    API->>DB: Require completed active entitlement

    Note over API,DB: 9.3 Revenue split ledger
    API->>DB: Idempotent purchase entry with commission and creator share
    alt Full refund
        Stripe->>API: Signed charge.refunded
        API->>DB: Revoke entitlement + reversing refund entry
    else Duplicate provider event
        API->>DB: Ignore already processed billing event
    end

    Note over Creator,Admin: 9.4 Payout onboarding and eligibility
    Creator->>API: Register provider account
    API->>DB: payout status = pending
    Admin->>API: Record provider-attested verification
    alt Creator approved and provider payout-ready
        API->>DB: payout status = verified
    else Unverified, restricted, or incomplete
        API-->>Admin: Reject payout eligibility
    end

    Note over API,Stripe: Marketplace finance is separate from organization subscription billing
